search in all fields: `[search:*[keyword]]`
search only in title: `[search:title[keyword]]`
search in tags: `[search:tags[keyword]]`
search only in field //myfield//: `[search:myfield[keyword]]`
search in several fields e.g. //myfield//, //yourfield//: `[search:myfield,yourfield[keyword]]`
search in title followed by search in text:`[search:title[foo]search:text[bar]]`